MZANSI has a rich variety of cultures and traditions. Ethnic and cultural diversity is what has kept the nation strong including the spirit of Ubuntu meaning "Humanity". Mzansi is also known for its attractive cultural attire, that symbolises uniqueness, confidence and pride. Zulu attire has been around for centuries - women at different stages of their lives wear different attire.The older they get and as they get married - the more they cover their bodies.Meanwhile the traditional dress for men consists of animal skins and feathers, the different kinds of skin indicates the status of the person wearing them.WATCH BELOW PICTURE:&nbsp;